OL,3,CSt Helier Constable backs
OL,4,Cinvestigation into Lido tender process
OL,6,FThe Constable of St Helier has backed
OL,7,Fcalls for an investigation into the
OL,8,FHavre des Pas Lido tender process
OL,9,Fafter concerns over how it was awarded
OL,10,Fto a private company.
OL,12,FJersey's government says the choice
OL,13,Fwas made after a thorough and fair
OL,14,Fassessment of all the options, but it
OL,15,Fhas seen a public backlash.
OL,17,FThe 'Love Our Lido' community group
OL,18,Fhad local support and initially
OL,19,Fpreferred bidding status.
