OL,3,CSt Helier Constable backs
OL,4,Cinvestigation into Lido tender process
OL,6,FAn independent panel then decided to
OL,7,Faward a nine-year contract to the
OL,8,Fprivate firm First Point, which said
OL,9,Fit could operate under the initial
OL,10,F#66,000 budget - while 'Love Our Lido'
OL,11,Fasked for a larger grant of #170,000.
OL,13,FHowever, St Helier Deputy David Warr
OL,14,Fsays: "I look at the #170,000 as a
OL,15,Fback stop, not how much money should
OL,16,Fbe spent. It's an insurance policy to
OL,17,Fprotect the governors in the event of
OL,18,Fa catastrophe on the site."
