OL,3,CSt Helier Constable backs
OL,4,Cinvestigation into Lido tender process
OL,6,FSimon Crowcroft, the Constable of St
OL,7,FHelier, oversaw the tender but says he
OL,8,Fkept a distance from the independent
OL,9,Fpanel.
OL,11,FHe adds: "I've listened carefully to
OL,12,Fsome of the criticisms of the tender
OL,13,Fprocess and I will be discussing those
OL,14,Fwith the Minister as soon as I can.
OL,16,F"Clearly, people feel the tender that
OL,17,Fwas preferred has not been treated
OL,18,Ffairly and it's important that we
OL,19,Finvestigate that to see if there's any
OL,20,Ftruth to it."
