OL,6,FITV News has contacted First Point but
OL,7,Fhas not yet received a response.
OL,9,FIn a statement on 31 October, they
OL,10,Fsaid: "We're honoured to be entrusted
OL,11,Fwith this cherished part of Jersey's
OL,12,Fheritage.
OL,14,F"Our vision is to preserve the Lido's
OL,15,Funique character while opening it up
OL,16,Ffor wider community use."
