OL,6,FMeanwhile, a public protest is planned
OL,7,Foutside Jersey States Chamber on
OL,8,FTuesday 11 November, as politicians
OL,9,Fwill debate Deputy Warr's proposition
OL,10,Fto scrap the current tender process
OL,11,Fand transfer the lease to 'Love Our
OL,12,FLido'.
